#### Connection Methods

**Using psql (Command Line)**:
```bash
PGPASSWORD="{{ db.access[0].password }}" psql \
  -h {{ db.endpoint }} \
  -U {{ db.access[0].username }} \
  -d {{ db.access[0].database }} \
  -p {{ db.port }}
```

**Connection String (for applications)** Keep in mind this is a private endpoint and not accessible from the public internet:
```
postgresql://{{ db.access[0].username }}:{{ db.access[0].password }}@{{ db.endpoint }}:{{ db.port }}/{{ db.access[0].database }}
```

